[0m[49m[39m   48,  32[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;9m-  49     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m **The problem:** The pseudocode publishes the full `ae_record` to SNS for high-severity alerts:
[0m[49m[38;5;9m-  50     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;9m-  51     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m ```text
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+       33[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Problem:** The pseudocode publishes the full `ae_record` to SNS:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+       34[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[39m   52,  35[0m:[39m[49m PUBLISH to SNS topic "ae-critical-alerts":
[0m[49m[39m   53,  36[0m:[39m[49m     subject: "High-severity adverse event detected"
