[0m[49m[38;5;10m+       47[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+       48[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Problem:** Neptune stores a graph linking patient_id nodes to drug nodes and adverse event nodes. This is PHI. The recipe mentions "requires VPC deployment" and "encryption at rest" but provides no guidance on:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+       49[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - IAM database authentication (Neptune supports this for fine-grained access)
